data.description: Luxury Lifestyle Home, located in central location minutes away from Westlake!  Beautiful Maintenance Free 2 Story Home with 4 Bedrooms, 2 1/2 Bathrooms. Great open floor plan with granite countertops, cherry cabinets, hardwood floors, crown molding and 9ft ceilings.  Extremely well maintained! Large rooms, nice established neighborhood!  Excellent location close to Smith Mountain Lake, short drive to Smith Mountain Lake county park that offers, beach, trails, public boat docks, playground.   and all of the Westlake amenities.  Amazing home for affordable price, with lots of sq ft and potential for more in lower level if needed or great storage! Won't last long, get inside, pictures do not do this home justice!
